               "text": "**Connecting Dark Mode Signal**\n\nI've just added a connection for the `darkModeChanged` signal. This updates the configuration button's icon based on the dark mode state, using appropriate SVG resources. I'm leveraging a lambda expression to handle the signal emission, making the code cleaner and more efficient.\n\n\n",
