            {
               "text": "The issue with the \"Config\" icon"
            },
            {
               "text": " being invisible in dark mode was due to the icon (`images/configure.svg`) having a dark fill color (`#23262"
            },
            {
               "text": "9`), which made it blend in with the dark background (`#2b2b2b`).\n\nI have implemented"
            },
            {
               "text": " the following changes to fix this:\n\n1.  **Icon Selection**: Modified `src/editor.cpp` to dynamically select "
            },
            {
               "text": "`images/configure_white.svg` when in dark mode and `images/configure.svg` otherwise.\n2."
            },
            {
               "text": "  **Dynamic Update**: Added a signal connection in `src/editor.cpp` to update the icon whenever the "
            },
            {
               "text": "`darkMode` state changes (`darkModeChanged` signal).\n3.  **CSS Cleanup**: Corrected the CSS selector in `src/dark"
            },
